    <templates>
        <template>
            <uuid>52cdafcc7fc44aa686e48e541ab2f796</uuid>
            <template>Template Windows Secure Boot Certificates</template>
            <name>Template Windows Secure Boot Certificates 2026</name>
            <description>Ueberwacht den Status der Windows Secure Boot Zertifikate (Ablauf 2026).

Referenzen:
- https://support.microsoft.com/de-de/topic/5062710
- https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/blog/windowsservernewsandbestpractices/windows-server-secure-boot-playbook-for-certificates-expiring-in-2026/4495789

Kompatibel mit Zabbix Agent 1 und Agent 2.

Installation:
1. Skript nach C:\Program Files\Zabbix Agent 2\zabbix-agent-scripts\check_secureboot_certs.ps1 kopieren
2. UserParameter eintragen:
   UserParameter=secureboot.status,powershell -NoProfile -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File "C:\Program Files\Zabbix Agent 2\zabbix-agent-scripts\check_secureboot_certs.ps1"
   Timeout=30
3. Zabbix Agent Dienst neu starten (benoetigt Admin-Rechte!)
4. Dieses Template dem Host zuweisen</description>
            <groups>
                <group>
                    <name>Templates/Security</name>
                </group>
            </groups>
            <items>
